the apartment in just a few days, Ove.

21:14.358 --> 21:16.568
Do you realize how big this is?

21:16.735 --> 21:18.862
She is here twice in six months.

21:19.029 --> 21:20.572
You'll be left with millions.

21:22.366 --> 21:25.410
With that kind of money
