and dressing on the side.

22:09.621 --> 22:11.331
As you wish. Thank you.

22:12.332 --> 22:15.293
Will you settle in Oslo now
or will you do a lot of commuting?

22:18.755 --> 22:21.550
Three and a half million,
plus stock options.

22:23.510 --> 22:25.345
