for granted, Greve.

22:25.512 --> 22:29.558
Don't forget you're a foreigner.
Norwegian companies would like...

22:29.725 --> 22:33.437
Roger. I don't doubt that your methods
will work on most people.

22:33.603 --> 22:35.188
