31:25.969 --> 31:28.888
I just wanted to hear your voice.

31:29.055 --> 31:30.890
That's sweet.

31:31.933 --> 31:33.768
Come and sit down.
This film just started.

31:33.935 --> 31:35.395
No.

31:36.479 --> 31:40.692
